With Roman Abramovich's era at Chelsea coming to an end, we look at the list of potential new owners. Todd Boehly; The US businessman and philanthropist already part-owns NBA team the LA Lakers and MLB's LA Dodgers. His net worth is estimated to be £6.6 billion and his £2.21 billion bid to buy the Blues in 2019 was turned down. Martin Broughton is also a potential buyer of Chelsea. The former British Airways and Liverpool FC chairman is reported to be a lifelong Chelsea fan.